<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Campus Hostel Allocation System</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://ai-public.creatie.ai/gen_page/tailwind-custom.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script
        src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com/3.4.5?plugins=forms@0.5.7,typography@0.5.13,aspect-ratio@0.4.2,container-queries@0.1.1"></script>
    <script src="https://ai-public.creatie.ai/gen_page/tailwind-config.min.js" data-color="#000000"
        data-border-radius="small"></script>
</head>

<body class="bg-gray-50 font-sans">
    <nav class="bg-white shadow-sm">
        <div class="max-w-8xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex justify-between h-16">
                <div class="flex">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center">
                        <span class="ml-3 text-xl font-semibold text-blue-900">Campus Hostel Allocation</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                    <a href="/login">

                        <button
                            class="!rounded-button bg-blue-700 text-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-indigo-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-custom">
                            Login
                        </button>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main>
        <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute inset-0">
                <img class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="/hero.jpg" alt="Campus">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gray-900 bg-opacity-50"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="relative max-w-8xl mx-auto py-24 px-4 sm:py-32 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">Find Your Perfect
                    Campus Home</h1>
                <p class="mt-6 text-xl text-gray-100 max-w-3xl">Experience hassle-free hostel allocation and roommate
                    matching based on your preferences. We make sure you're paired with compatible roommates for the
                    best campus living experience.</p>
                <div class="mt-10">
                    <a href="/login"><button
                        class="!rounded-button bg-blue-700 text-white px-8 py-3 text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-indigo-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-custom">
                        Get Started
                    </button></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-8xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto">
                <h2 class="text-center text-3xl font-extrabold text-blue-900">How It Works</h2>
                <p class="mt-4 text-center text-blue-900">Simple steps to find your perfect room and roommate match</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-16">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
                    <div class="relative p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-blue-700 bg-opacity-10 rounded-md">
                            <i class="fas fa-user-circle text-blue-900 text-xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-medium text-blue-900">1. Login</h3>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-blue-900">Sign in with your student credentials</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="relative p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-blue-700 bg-opacity-10 rounded-md"> <i
                                class="fas fa-sliders text-blue-900 text-xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-medium text-blue-900">2. Set Preferences</h3>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-blue-900">Choose your preferences for room conditions and living habits to
                            find compatible matches.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="relative p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-blue-700 bg-opacity-10 rounded-md"> <i
                                class="fas fa-home text-blue-900 text-xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-medium text-blue-900">3. Get Matched</h3>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-blue-900">Our system automatically assigns you to the perfect room based on
                            your preferences.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-8xl mx-auto py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="mt-8 border-t border-gray-200 pt-8 md:flex md:items-center md:justify-between">
                <div class="flex space-x-6 md:order-2"> <a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-blue-900">
                        <i class="fab fa-facebook"></i> </a>
                    <a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-blue-900">
                        <i class="fab fa-twitter"></i>
                    </a>
                    <a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-blue-900">
                        <i class="fab fa-instagram"></i>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <p class="mt-8 text-base text-gray-400 md:mt-0 md:order-1">
                    &copy; 2025 Campus Hostel Allocation. All rights reserved.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>